name: Cow Duck Fever (James Davis)
description:
Cow Duck Fever Up Arrow or W - Jump or tap right side of screen Space - Change between Cow or Duck or Tap left side of screen Cow: Jumps higher but is taller
Duck: Jumps lower but is short Objective

An endless runner where you can switch between a duck and a cow. Becomes more difficult the further you get. Jump through as many hoops as you can!

Is your high score better than your friends? ;)
